28
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:53,720
Honestly, I don't know either.

29
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:54,520
You don't?

30
00:00:56,790 --> 00:00:57,840
So what do we do then?

31
00:00:58,880 --> 00:00:59,270
Neither

32
00:00:59,270 --> 00:01:00,150
of us know.

33
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:00,890
You don't either?

34
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:02,720
Let me hear your thoughts first.

35
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:05,720
Everyone says
I should listen to Yang more.

36
00:01:06,550 --> 00:01:07,910
I'll hear what Yang thinks first.

37
00:01:07,910 --> 00:01:08,270
I will

38
