39
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,120
Like when we play games.

40
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:12,270
On this, I'll hear your take first.

41
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:13,880
Does your affection

42
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:15,400
