45
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,390
Right now, it's more about feelings.

46
00:01:20,390 --> 00:01:21,120
Why's that?

47
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:23,550
No idea.

48
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:25,950
It just feels right, relaxing.

49
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:27,720
It feels different.

50
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:29,830
I feel the same way.

51
00:01:31,590 --> 00:01:32,680
Come take a walk with me.

52
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,440
Let's go.

53
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,590
I'll change my shoes first.

54
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:37,720
