61
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:51,590
No way.

62
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:52,160
Really?

63
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:52,830
Yeah, really not.

64
00:01:53,270 --> 00:01:54,720
Please don't film my feet, okay?

65
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,440
Cameramen.

66
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:55,870
(Mosaic)

67
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:56,700
(Alright)
Let's go.

68
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,310
This way,

69
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,720
I'm much taller.

70
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,480
Why the laughter?

71
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,760
Since when did you get an ego?

72
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,360
Well,

73
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:04,400
it's because...

74
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:04,870
It's funny.

75
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:06,360
Because standing like this will...

76
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:06,950
Well, you know.

77
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,160
Or it'll end up like this.

78
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:10,700
