84
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:18,030
Forget it.

85
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:19,620
(Let's drop this topic.)

86
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:21,210
Let's sit over here.

87
00:02:21,830 --> 00:02:22,360
Sit properly.

88
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,670
So about that matter,

89
00:02:26,670 --> 00:02:27,750
honestly, I still

90
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,000
want to hear what you think.

91
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,550
Which matter?

92
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,320
About leaving the island.

93
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,880
When I was still here,
I didn't think much about it.

94
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,240
I won't think about...

95
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,490
But once you leave the island...

96
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:39,080
Yes.

97
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,720
A strong sense of withdrawal.

98
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,290
It's not like

99
00:02:43,290 --> 00:02:44,370
whenever I want to see you,

100
00:02:44,370 --> 00:02:46,240
I can just walk up to your dorm,

101
00:02:46,670 --> 00:02:47,760
knock on your door,

102
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:49,200
and everything would be sorted out.

103
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:53,630
Right?

104
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:59,600
So, there are three possible solutions.

105
00:03:00,270 --> 00:03:00,720
First,

106
00:03:01,110 --> 00:03:02,090
I move to your city.

107
00:03:02,090 --> 00:03:03,120
Second, you move to mine.

108
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,800
Third, we both start fresh in a new city.

109
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,000
No other options.

110
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,470
So long distance is impossible.

111
00:03:10,910 --> 00:03:11,630
What do you mean?

112
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:12,320
No long distance.

113
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,870
You want a long-distance thing forever?

114
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,960
That's even less possible.

115
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:20,000
Then...

116
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,190
The fourth option.

117
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:22,440
We just stay long distance.

118
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,320
Stay that way and...

119
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,190
see how it'd work.

120
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,390
Yeah, and maybe I'll...

121
00:03:25,390 --> 00:03:26,440
If I ever hit the jackpot,

122
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,800
win billions, then maybe

123
00:03:27,830 --> 00:03:29,670
(Fantasy moment)
we'd travel around the world.

124
00:03:29,670 --> 00:03:30,720
That's one possible future,

125
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,030
